OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778746039
OL,3,CElderly woman, 89, killed in car crash
OL,5,FAn 89-year-old woman has been killed
OL,6,Fin a crash in Worthing.
OL,8,FThe collision, involving a BMW and a
OL,9,Fsilver Ford Focus Estate, happened on
OL,10,Fthe A2032 at about 1.35pm on Tuesday,
OL,11,F12th May.
OL,13,FThe 89-year-old woman, who was a
OL,14,Fpassenger in the BMW, was pronounced
OL,15,Fdeceased at the scene. Her next of kin
OL,16,Fhave been informed.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
