OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778746039
OL,3,CElderly woman, 89, killed in car crash
OL,5,FThe driver of the Ford Focus, a 21-
OL,6,Fyear-old man, was arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of causing death by
OL,8,Fdangerous driving and taken into
OL,9,Fcustody.
OL,11,FThe A2032 was closed in both
OL,12,Fdirections from the junction with
OL,13,FLindum Road and the roundabout with
OL,14,FThe Boulevard and Durrington Lane for
OL,15,Fseveral hours while emergency services
OL,16,Fresponded to the incident.
